The paper presents a machine-checked soundness proof of a translation of Event-B to the Java Modeling Language (JML), which involves formal verification and programming languages. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also involves formalisation and proof, which suggests the possibility of cs.PL (Programming Languages) and cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). Additionally, the paper deals with refinement and simulation, which are topics in cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) and cs.ET (Emerging Technologies).
